HEADWORD: Metacrolein
<hw>Met`a*cro"le*in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>met-</ets> + <ets>acrolein</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
polymeric modification of acrolein obtained by heating it with caustic
